00:01:00,375 --> 00:01:01,958
[LIGIER] Yeah, we can
head there together.

5
00:01:02,041 --> 00:01:03,250
I can't just leave in the middle

6
00:01:03,333 --> 00:01:04,708
of Durandal's
maintenance routine.

7
00:01:04,791 --> 00:01:06,541
I'll meet you there later.

8
00:01:06,625 --> 00:01:08,541
But you don't want to
miss out on all the fun!

9
00:01:08,625 --> 00:01:11,833
Yeah, jeez. Is it hard to hear
with your head up your ass?

10
00:01:11,916 --> 00:01:14,666
[SUBARU sighs]

11
