[SUBARU]
No one's come to get me.

35
00:02:30,291 --> 00:02:33,458
It's mean to keep me
in suspense for so long.

36
00:02:33,541 --> 00:02:35,375
I wonder what's wrong.

37
00:02:35,458 --> 00:02:38,750
