to go check on them.

41
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:52,000
[SUBARU]
I didn't see them anywhere.

42
00:02:52,083 --> 00:02:53,875
What's going on?

43
00:02:53,958 --> 00:02:56,708
Was I totally off-base?

44
00:03:00,375 --> 00:03:03,208
[music plays]

45
00:03:05,666 --> 00:03:07,250
[VULGAR]
5... 6... 7... 8...

46
00:03:07,333 --> 00:03:08,541
