47
00:03:12,125 --> 00:03:15,333
[music continues]

48
00:03:17,166 --> 00:03:19,416
[SUBARU]
I know what this is!

49
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:22,166
One of those flash-mob things!

50
00:03:26,625 --> 00:03:29,958
[SUBARU] They choreographed
a dance number just for me!

51
00:03:30,041 --> 00:03:31,083
Wait...

52
00:03:31,166 --> 00:03:34,250
[LIGIER chattering]

53
00:03:34,333 --> 00:03:37,541
[SUBARU]
Huh? Huh?!

54
00:03:37,625 --> 00:03:40,333
Huh...?!

55
00:03:40,416 --> 00:03:43,125
If this is my birthday surprise

56
00:03:43,208 --> 00:03:47,083
then why isn't anybody
looking at me?!

57
00:03:47,166 --> 00:03:48,375
[ALL]
Way to go!

58
00:03:48,458 --> 00:03:50,291
Congrats on your marriage!

59
00:03:50,375 --> 00:03:53,541
Thanks so much!
What a great surprise!

60
00:03:53,625 --> 00:03:54,916
You sons a bitches!

61
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,083
That was great! Thanks, guys.

62
00:03:57,166 --> 00:03:59,375
[PAC2-AR] Here's to a long
and happy life together!

63
00:03:59,458 --> 00:04:00,625
Hip-hip-hooray!

64
00:04:00,708 --> 00:04:03,083
It really worked?
You were surprised?

65
00:04:03,166 --> 00:04:06,333
[AVANTI]
Are you kidding? Totally!

66
00:04:06,416 --> 00:04:10,333
[SUBARU] I was surprised
the surprise wasn't for me.

67
00:04:10,416 --> 00:04:12,208
[PAC2-AR] I'm so proud of
everybody coming together

68
00:04:12,291 --> 00:04:13,625
to make this a success!

69
00:04:13,708 --> 00:04:16,375
Almost the entire crew
is here to celebrate.

70
00:04:16,458 --> 00:04:17,916
[SUBARU]
