71
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,958
[gasps]

72
00:04:20,166 --> 00:04:23,041
[SUBARU]
Okay. Some couple got married,

73
00:04:23,125 --> 00:04:26,000
and that's relevant to me how?

74
00:04:27,541 --> 00:04:28,916
[SUBARU]
That email!

75
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:33,250
How was I supposed to know
it was something important?

76
00:04:33,333 --> 00:04:34,583
[CREW chattering]

77
00:04:34,666 --> 00:04:37,416
[PAC2-AR] Their happiness
is contagious, isn't it?

78
00:04:39,041 --> 00:04:43,625
[SUBARU]
♪ Happy birthday to me ♪

79
00:04:43,708 --> 00:04:47,500
♪ Happy birthday to me ♪

80
00:04:47,583 --> 00:04:49,666
♪ Happy birthday dear ♪

81
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:52,958
♪ Lieutenant Junior Grade
Subaru Ichinose ♪

82
00:04:53,041 --> 00:04:55,375
[SUBARU]
