83
00:04:55,458 --> 00:04:58,291
Why was I born in
the first place?

84
00:04:58,375 --> 00:05:00,166
Nobody seems to care.

85
00:05:00,250 --> 00:05:02,375
It's like they don't
even need me.

86
00:05:02,458 --> 00:05:03,666
[beeping]

87
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:07,625
[SUBARU]
Uh. An enemy attack? Now?

88
00:05:07,708 --> 00:05:10,666
Subaru Ichinose,
sortieing in the Durandal!

89
00:05:15,083 --> 00:05:16,458
[SUBARU]
How did so many of them get here

90
00:05:16,541 --> 00:05:18,708
without anyone noticing?

91
00:05:18,791 --> 00:05:21,666
They're all too busy with
their dumb surprise party.

92
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:24,333
No one even noticed
it was my birthday!

93
00:05:24,416 --> 00:05:26,791
I deserve a celebration, too!

94
00:05:26,875 --> 00:05:29,166
[SUBARU yells]

95
00:05:31,583 --> 00:05:32,750
[SUBARU]
I should've known.

96
00:05:32,833 --> 00:05:34,583
They don't care about me!

97
00:05:34,666 --> 00:05:36,791
You're my only friend, Durandal.

98
00:05:39,958 --> 00:05:41,291
That's it!

99
00:05:54,583 --> 00:05:59,166
